hopobject.body: I like watching TV helix dna stock The BlackBerry Q5 isn’t as impressive a handset as I would have liked it to be. There’s a distinct lack of excitement about the build, and the small screen compromises use – we’ve simply outgrown this screen size for many tasks. If you really need BlackBerry 10 and have a Curve or Bold then think carefully about sticking with your old handset until you can afford the much better Q10 or Z10.
